#: ../../../driver-api/media/tx-rx.rst:49
msgid ""
"The :ref:`V4L2_CID_LINK_FREQ <v4l2-cid-link-freq>` control is used to tell "
"the receiver the frequency of the bus (i.e. it is not the same as the symbol "
"rate)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/media/tx-rx.rst:52
msgid ""
"Drivers that do not have user-configurable link frequency should report it "
"through the ``.get_mbus_config()`` subdev pad operation, in the "
"``link_freq`` field of struct v4l2_mbus_config, instead of through controls."
